{"id": "1517291143698583783", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "451986936635326474", "author_name": "ymarsakar", "author_bot": false, "content": "Investigation-D-Effect Zone: Wave 4: Alert III Battle Replay\nKeeper: Ymarsakar（100996499）\n\nMouchette, Doomsday Rampage, Hand of Oblivion, Dream of Medicine\nGoliath, Amidst the Downpour, Hope, Burial Ground's Sighs\nLotan, Celestial Beast, Impending Sun, Scarlet Embrace\nCeleste, Sail of Providence, Frenzy, Life Drain\nGiant's Reign\n\nb414732d-d405-3d35-b324-243588b39d36#E#a", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T22:13:18.564000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1517292497313992857", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "451986936635326474", "author_name": "ymarsakar", "author_bot": false, "content": "我忘了使用那个能降低敌人强度的稀有轮盘。如果用了的话，肯定会帮上大忙。不过这次实验还是成功的。有一个与穆谢特配合的连招，可以回收之前的攻击卡，这和洛坦或歌利亚的免费“崇高”攻击卡配合得很好。如果有人想看回放，文中附有链接。\n\n对于这样一支投入极低的队伍来说，我竟然在第一次尝试就通关了所有关卡，尽管治疗者的能力本可以更强一些。多亏了塞莱斯特的“复活”和“死亡复活”，我才勉强撑了下来。讽刺的是，拥有3名实力雄厚的输出角色意味着“狩猎标记”并不总是问题，但BOSS确实会严惩那些使用特定卡牌的玩家。穆谢特并不需要那个契约，一个伤害加成卡会更好。", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T22:18:41.291000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1517293108541522132", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "451986936635326474", "author_name": "ymarsakar", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的，这是标准打法，但也有一些变招，可以利用敌方BOSS的弱点，并结合特定的队伍搭配。我来给你演示一两种，或者三两种。", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T22:21:07.019000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["489362923991334913"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1517197545489698936", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
